    rdfs:comment "The subset of wr:substance the Water Quality Archive's observations actually cover here, and therefore the only ones a time-series chart can draw. Membership is a fact about the OBSERVATION SET, not about the permits: a determinand outside this scheme is still regulated, still has a limit, and is still a condition of the permit - nobody has measured it." ;
    skos:prefLabel "Regulated determinands the catchment holds a time series for" .

